{"tid":2254119,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"露宿者小欖離奇亡 CCTV片交警方","createTime":"2020-10-22T14:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T15:10:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"548b56ef0926bd235319f7b8c844191398e774b8","tid":2254119,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201022/E5OB6WREWZFWFA5NJVEK2XF27E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201022%2FE5OB6WREWZFWFA5NJVEK2XF27E%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRCYtkWzW%2FBkyQE6eFpzr100%3D&h=7cd96cce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201022%2FE5OB6WREWZFWFA5NJVEK2XF27E%2F&h=66513dd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201022/E5OB6WREWZFWFA5NJVEK2XF27E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n露宿者小欖離奇亡 CCTV片交警方<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】曾遭警暴的露宿者黎民十（阿十）月初在小欖精神病治療中心被發現長褲纏頸，送院後身亡。事件疑點重重，社福界立法會議員邵家臻及林國璋牧師等人昨日召開記者會，交代阿十的身後事。邵家臻批評懲教署承認掌握阿十囚房的閉路電視片段，卻遲遲未有回覆會否妥善保存，促請署方主動公開相關片段，以釋除公眾疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ubHQODNnEiwHXYzfj7YYAZ4fC1c=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XCLI5UI2GJBSRKX32DEY4UVIDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FubHQODNnEiwHXYzfj7YYAZ4fC1c%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXCLI5UI2GJBSRKX32DEY4UVIDQ.jpg&h=c219c23c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■左起：何啟明、林國璋、邵家臻及張超雄昨向阿十默哀致意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同鄉設壇致祭<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻貿疑，被送入小欖精神病治療中心的囚友均會被列在醫療觀察名單上，職員會每15分鐘巡邏一次，並在記錄冊上簽名確認。阿十據指是被囚禁於俗稱「棉花房」的防止自殺護墊房間，當時囚友仍未換季只穿短褲，因此他不可能用長褲自殺。<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻說，懲教署已承認阿十身處的「棉花房」有閉路電視，相信署方掌握事發經過。他。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於阿十的殮葬安排，一直協助露宿者的林國璋牧師稱，早前收到阿十家人的信件，請求他代為辦理後事，待驗屍及火化完成後，林會將其骨灰帶回越南安葬。在阿十生前露宿的位置，其越南同鄉為他設起小型祭壇，香爐上插滿香。。。。。。。。。。訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/r6mlpDl4h0zxvskAse3Y41HX9Ys=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NCWTRTTYS5H53DBI2ADCI6CN5Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fr6mlpDl4h0zxvskAse3Y41HX9Ys%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNCWTRTTYS5H53DBI2ADCI6CN5Q.jpg&h=e08f8d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■越南同鄉表示，阿十性格隨和開朗，故無法相信他會在獄中自殺。"},{"pid":"b52ed696ecad9ce4b682d098e4123f7f1e4065e4","tid":2254119,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:54:43.000Z","msg":"冇可疑<br />\n<br />\nClose file"},{"pid":"9afb5c03465e3b9a7205297cc71f249d77da08db","tid":2254119,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:57:22.000Z","msg":"冇可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8341c75967484a750c659ee2cffb591c7eb905f","tid":2254119,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:08:44.000Z","msg":"交返比個殺人犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c68d62298e7113357b434fe5aef4994276055f3","tid":2254119,"uid":300592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:09:40.000Z","msg":"交俾警方剪接？"},{"pid":"916aebb85bd9424c079aadf96f0c1499c9b3aeb7","tid":2254119,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:10:45.000Z","msg":"「亞十被自殺案」黑警今次呢單野算唔算偽造證供？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2253641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2253641</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}